293
00:15:27.896 --> 00:15:31.204
Oh. yeah. I'll. uh... Uh. one sec. Yeah.

294
00:15:33.701 --> 00:15:34.790
I'll tell you later.

295
00:15:38.785 --> 00:15:41.220
- Okay. Get some rest.
- All right. Dad. Look. Dad. I'm good.

296
00:15:41.231 --> 00:15:42.885
