330
00:17:08.999 --> 00:17:12.017
[EXHALES]

331
00:17:12.148 --> 00:17:13.845
Well. I got some good news.

332
00:17:14.089 --> 00:17:17.745
We. uh. pulled something
out of that thing...

333
00:17:18.917 --> 00:17:21.659
