334
00:17:23.135 --> 00:17:24.995
So you think it's like a poison?

335
00:17:25.006 --> 00:17:26.202
Well. it could be.

336
00:17:26.213 --> 00:17:28.833
The only problem is we gotta
figure out how to get this

337
00:17:28.844 --> 00:17:31.966
