361
00:18:44.060 --> 00:18:45.633
- Listen. we gotta talk.
- I have to go.

362
00:18:45.644 --> 00:18:47.711
- Huh? Nah. Come here.
- [ETHAN] Hey. what're you doing?

363
00:18:47.722 --> 00:18:48.910
