- We made a deal. remember?

364
00:18:48.921 --> 00:18:50.782
I play you the song. you
tell me about the symbol.

365
00:18:50.793 --> 00:18:52.282
Hey! Leave him alone.

366
00:18:52.382 --> 00:18:53.988
