longer than 10 minutes?

390
00:19:56.312 --> 00:19:57.672
Great. you're yelling at me again.

391
00:19:57.683 --> 00:19:59.804
- Fuck off.
- That didn't take very long.

392
00:20:00.072 --> 00:20:01.247
Victor!

393
00:20:04.500 --> 00:20:06.459
